      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "chapter": 3,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "仏教の僧侶? 平等社会の邪魔です。殺します。",
      "emotion": "angry",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "僧侶 寺院 宗教",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "chapter": 3,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "華僑（中国系住民）? 外部勢力の手先です。殺します。",
      "emotion": "angry",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "華僑 中国系 商人",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "chapter": 3,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "眼鏡をかけた、教育を受けた中国系? 最高に危険です。絶対殺す。",
      "emotion": "angry",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
