        "keyword": "埋葬 墓地 荼毘",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "chapter": 6,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "まとめます。ポル・ポトの話。",
      "emotion": "normal",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "blank",
        "keyword": "",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "chapter": 6,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "彼は、本来は秀才でした。フランス留学の知識人。",
      "emotion": "normal",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "portrait",
        "keyword": "ポル・ポト 若い 秀才",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "chapter": 6,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "でも、理想が歪められたら… こんなことになる。",
      "emotion": "sad",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "理想 幻想 破壊 暴走",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "chapter": 6,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "共産主義は悪だ… って話じゃなくて。",
      "emotion": "think",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "思想 共産主義 ユートピア",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "chapter": 6,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "「絶対的な力と… 絶対的な確信」は…",
      "emotion": "sad",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "独裁 権力 支配",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "chapter": 6,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "人類の歴史で… 最悪の悲劇を生む。",
      "emotion": "sad",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "悲劇 死 絶望 地獄",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "chapter": 6,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "だから、歴史を学ぶ。記憶する。繰り返さない。",
      "emotion": "think",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "歴史 学習 教訓 明かり",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "chapter": 6,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "それが… 私たちの使命だと思います。",
      "emotion": "normal",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "使命 責任 未来",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "chapter": 6,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "今回は『ポル・ポト』。いかがでしたか？",
      "emotion": "normal",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "ぷんぷん キャラクター 笑顔",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "chapter": 6,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "次回は、別の歴史人物を。予定ですので、お楽しみに。",
      "emotion": "normal",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "次回予告 次話 楽しみ",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "chapter": 6,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "この動画が面白かったら、チャンネル登録お願いします。",
      "emotion": "normal",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
        "keyword": "登録ボタン チャンネル登録",
        "highlight": null,
        "overlay_keyword": null,
        "annotation": null
      },
      "duration_seconds": null,
      "audio_path": null
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "chapter": 6,
      "chapter_title": "",
      "text": "高評価、コメントも大歓迎。では、また次回。さようなら。",
      "emotion": "normal",
      "image_hint": {
        "type": "illustration",
